Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides Bowling Alley. My name is Jamie. How can I assist you today?

Hi Jamie, I'm trying to sort out some billing issues I've encountered. My name is Sam.

Thank you for reaching out, Sam. I'd be happy to help. Could you please provide your account number, spelled out?

Certainly. My account number is three five seven two zero one.

Great, thank you. To verify your identity, could you also provide the zip code associated with your account?

Sure, it’s zero two six six eight.

Thanks, Sam. I see the issue here. It looks like there was a slight overcharge on your last bill. I can process a refund for you. It should be reflected in your account within five to seven business days.

Oh, that’s a relief. Thank you for sorting that out so quickly!

You're welcome, Sam. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

No, that was all. Thanks for your help, Jamie!

Anytime, Sam. Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
